menu "Hall Effect Sensor"

    config HALL_SENSOR_DEFAULT_GPIO
        int "Default GPIO for Hall sensor input"
        default 10
        range 0 21
        help
            GPIO pin connected to the Hall effect sensor output.
            The pin is configured as an input with an internal pull-up.

    config HALL_SENSOR_PULSES_PER_REV
        int "Pulses per revolution"
        default 4
        range 1 32
        help
            Number of magnets (pulses) per full revolution of the rotor.
            Set this to match the number of magnets mounted on the water brake.

endmenu
